        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="e8V0I1YszctLmOaIzzUB-10" value="&lt;div style=&quot;padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;PROBABILITY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Implementing these controls is estimated to reduce the asset&#39;s vulnerability by &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;13&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;106&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;80%&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;. While these measures effectively neutralize common automated attacks and human error, a residual risk remains regarding highly sophisticated or experienced attackers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=14;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="550" y="760" width="500" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="e8V0I1YszctLmOaIzzUB-11" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; padding-right: 25px; padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;padding-right: 25px; padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;WELL FORMED RISK STATEMENT&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;padding-right: 25px; padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify; padding-right: 25px; padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;A malicious external actor may exploit the use of company laptops in home environments where technical security knowledge and web-filtering are currently insufficient. By accessing unblocked malicious websites, an attacker could compromise the device or the network switch to gain unauthorized entry into the system. This vulnerability poses a direct threat to the confidentiality of sensitive data, including delivery receipts, sales invoices, and legal contracts. To mitigate this, the company will implement strict web-filtering and limit remote accessibility to secure the network perimeter. Additionally, comprehensive employee training on modern malware will be conducted to address the human element of this risk. These combined efforts are projected to reduce the overall vulnerability of company assets by 80%. Consequently, only highly sophisticated and experienced attackers would remain a significant threat to the organization.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=14;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="37.5" y="1040" width="1015" height="310" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
